{"tid":48258,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違例BMW被警追到撞閘 男司機女乘客走唔甩","createTime":"2016-12-21T03:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T03:27:07.000Z","uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35273c4f73bcdabff7c442e08f2787feeee3561c","tid":48258,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:19:11.000Z","msg":"凌晨3時許，一輛寶馬由男司機駕駛，載同一名女乘客，沿大埔吐露港公路南行，駛至康樂園附近在雙白線切線，其間新界北交通特遣隊，在場進行反酒駕行動，警員發現指示司機停車接受檢查，但司機不理會並加速逃去。警方展開追截。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬沿吐露港公路轉入南運路，其間衝了4次紅燈，並且逆線駛入汀角路，行駛200米至汀角路51a至57號太平工業中心1座時，雙方追逐約3.1公里，終被追截警車逼入停車場，停下時撞到一道鐵閘。<br />\n事後司機下車逃走，留下23歲女乘客在車上。警方增援包圍工廈搜查，從25樓往地下搜索，在4樓梯間尋獲涉案姓王46歲司機。他涉嫌無牌駕駛、沒有第三者保險及危險駕駛，女乘客則違反感化令。兩人被警方拘捕，帶返警署調查。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56072920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56072920&d=y%2BZDlISUvbTxSxmXlt41VRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=4cc8cfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56072920&h=414bab40\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56072920</a>"},{"pid":"470301e788a16e67306267f5b4a471610bbeb0e0","tid":48258,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"無牌揸到咁耐"},{"pid":"dfe3e0d48749cd1e017ffd2a5d57420107a0b6e9","tid":48258,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無牌揸到咁耐</blockquote><br />\n揸自動波好易啫  同埋佢應該唔係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963f9a8bf9af04793523d35b95952c5cdd2a8d71","tid":48258,"uid":39141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"無一個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dd58eb050c73c7f7c0a1ee86bf22db93d09a88","tid":48258,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit